---
title: Grilled Hawaiian Shoyu-Style Tofu with Fluffy Rice and Foil-Pouch Veggies
description: Hawaiian shoyu tofu is an island-style comfort food! Simmer tofu in a flavourful mix of soy, mirin, brown sugar, ginger and garlic! Once cooked through, grill and baste the tofu with its braising liquid! Want to prep ahead? Braise the tofu ahead of time, cool and refrigerate, then reheat on the grill when you're ready to serve!
